{
  "texts": [
    "Is Julius the (or a) creator of the essay he hands in?",
    "If so, why?",
    "And if not, who is?This is an instance where creatorship and authorship importantly come apart, and CCC can help us unpack the distinction.",
    "Three features of CCC, in particular, are vital here: originality, independence and control.",
    "Let us first turn to originality, and generously assume that Julius had some original ideas for how to best prompt ChatGPT to generate the kind of text that would be useful to put a passing essay together-but did not apply any subject knowledge relevant to the essay."
  ]
}